OL,6,FIranians are trapped between bombs and
OL,7,Fcrackdowns.
OL,9,F"Where am I supposed to go?" Fatemeh
OL,10,Fasks me.
OL,12,FSince I first reported on Iran in
OL,13,F2022, I have met, interviewed and
OL,14,Fremained in touch with dozens of
OL,15,Fpeople in the country.
