OL,3,CTrapped between bombs and crackdowns:
OL,4,CIranians wrestle with decision to flee
OL,6,FI have no answer for Fatemeh's
OL,7,Fquestion. I have never been to Iran. I
OL,8,Fknow where she lives - the capital
OL,9,Fcity of Tehran - but I have no idea
OL,10,Fwhere is safe and where isn't right
OL,11,Fnow.
OL,13,FAn Iranian neighbour of mine in London
OL,14,Fhas been checking in on his extended
OL,15,Ffamily living in Tehran, every day
OL,16,Fsince Friday.
OL,18,F"Everyone is out of harm's way. But
OL,19,Fthis is all pretty awful, and sad to
OL,20,Fbe honest."
