OL,3,CTrapped between bombs and crackdowns:
OL,4,CIranians wrestle with decision to flee
OL,6,FThis morning, he couldn't get in touch
OL,7,Fwith anyone. The internet was down,
OL,8,Fand phone lines were dead.
OL,10,FCommunication is so often patchy in
OL,11,FIran, and when it comes alive again,
OL,12,FIranians often reach out - even to
OL,13,Fveritable strangers like me - so
OL,14,Fpeople hear their voices, and know
OL,15,Fwhat is happening to them.
