OL,3,CTrapped between bombs and crackdowns:
OL,4,CIranians wrestle with decision to flee
OL,6,FWe can't tell the stories of the
OL,7,FIranian people easily, because
OL,8,Fjournalists are rarely allowed inside
OL,9,Fthe country, whereas we can speak
OL,10,Fdirectly to Israelis being attacked,
OL,11,Fbecause ITV News has reporters and
OL,12,Fproducers there.
OL,14,FSince Friday, many people have been
OL,15,Ftrying to escape Iran. Turkey and
OL,16,FArmenia being the favoured routes.
OL,17,FIt's quicker to get there from Tehran,
OL,18,Fand once they're there, they can fly
OL,19,Fmore easily to other countries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
