OL,3,CTrapped between bombs and crackdowns:
OL,4,CIranians wrestle with decision to flee
OL,6,FBabak, who is 41, left Tehran two days
OL,7,Fago. Today, he finally reached Yerevan
OL,8,Fin Armenia.
OL,10,F"I spent one day in the car," he says.
OL,11,F"Tehran to Tabriz took 12 hours. I
OL,12,Fswitched cars there, then another four
OL,13,Fhours to the Armenian border.
OL,15,F"I walked for about an hour, got
OL,16,Fanother car, and it took us 10 hours
OL,17,Fto reach Yerevan. The road is narrow
OL,18,Fand dangerous. We drove through the
OL,19,Fnight on dangerous roads ` I wouldn't
OL,20,Frecommend it."
