OL,3,CTrapped between bombs and crackdowns:
OL,4,CIranians wrestle with decision to flee
OL,6,FBabak was visiting family in Iran on a
OL,7,Fholiday. Now, he's hoping to find a
OL,8,Fflight back to Canada.
OL,10,FIt is Tehran that has been hit hardest
OL,11,Fso far. In the capital, there is fear
OL,12,Fof bombs, fear of arrest by the
OL,13,Fregime, and fear of silence.
OL,15,FThirty-year-old Farideh crossed into
OL,16,FTurkey on foot.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
