OL,11,FKaveh is 42. He owns a small cafe in
OL,12,FTehran, and says he's staying put,
OL,13,Feven as others around him flee.
OL,15,F"I feel responsible for my staff. Some
OL,16,Fhave young kids, others are caring for
OL,17,Felderly parents. They can't travel.
OL,18,FI'll stay behind to help."
