OL,3,CTrapped between bombs and crackdowns:
OL,4,CIranians wrestle with decision to flee
OL,6,FFear doesn't just come from the skies.
OL,7,FThe government's war on dissent hasn't
OL,8,Fpaused just because missiles have
OL,9,Frained.
OL,11,FHossein is a filmmaker.
OL,13,FHe said: "No one cares about us. I'm
OL,14,Fconstantly thinking, will I be killed
OL,15,Fby a bomb? Or will I be arrested
OL,16,Ffirst? We, as Iranian people, only
OL,17,Fhave each other. That's it."
