OL,3,CTrapped between bombs and crackdowns:
OL,4,CIranians wrestle with decision to flee
OL,6,FWith the internet down and news hard
OL,7,Fto verify, people rely on scraps of
OL,8,Finformation delivered via voice notes,
OL,9,Ftexts, and coded messages.
OL,11,FMy phone illuminates again. This time
OL,12,Fwith an audio message from Minoo,
OL,13,Ftelling me about her journey out.
OL,15,FHearing the voice of a woman, of a
OL,16,Fsimilar age to me, recounting her
OL,17,Fjourney and her thinking stopped me in
OL,18,Fmy tracks. Minoo is an architect who
OL,19,Fstarted her escape to Armenia two days
OL,20,Fago, never believing this would happen.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
