OL,3,CTrapped between bombs and crackdowns:
OL,4,CIranians wrestle with decision to flee
OL,6,FMinoo's choice to flee is one she has
OL,7,Fmade reluctantly. Iran is where she
OL,8,Fwas born, where she went to school,
OL,9,Fwhere she grew up, where she got
OL,10,Fmarried and where she has carved out
OL,11,Fher career.
OL,13,FIt is the country she loves and never
OL,14,Fthought she'd leave.
